creator: Xun Hay
descriptionHtml:
🔥 It’s a narrative game with lots of levels and tricky tasks.

💥The lovers need your help. You’ll need all your courage and mother wit to solve the puzzles . They try to escape the building and makes a lot of vital choices. We hope you will help them to be together.

🤗🤗Make a choice and find a way out.
descriptionShort: Make the correct choice and save the lovers to help them together
title: Save The Lover : Tricky Puzzle
